<!-- \procedure — English alias for the TW5 \procedure pragma.
     Hawaiian equivalent: wehe (procedure/function executor; outside/exit boundary).
     lar-see-also: wehe

     <<~ \procedure name(params) >>body<<~/ \procedure >> declares a named
     procedure in memetic-wikitext. The sigil form IS the declaration mechanism —
     it produces no render output of its own (lar-kind: pragma-alias).

     Operator-readable: <<~ \procedure greet(name:"world") >>Hello <<name>>!<<~/ \procedure >>
     Same semantic as native TW5: \procedure greet(name:"world") Hello <<name>>! \end -->
